  "detailed_description": "Hexton is a relaxing city building game. Let your mind drift as you progressively build an idyllic little town.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A casual strategy game</h2>The better you arrange you buildings, the more items you will produce and the longer you will be able to last. If you run out of items, it's game over!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/ab8ac993aee011f439d8afabfb32711c.poster.avif?t=1715970146\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/ab8ac993aee011f439d8afabfb32711c.webm?t=1715970146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/ab8ac993aee011f439d8afabfb32711c.mp4?t=1715970146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless replayability</h2>Experience a very casual city builder with endless replayability and a suprising level of complexity. It will take you seconds to grasp this game but hours to truely master it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/ee30545b354768113daf78e066989709.poster.avif?t=1715970146\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/ee30545b354768113daf78e066989709.webm?t=1715970146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/ee30545b354768113daf78e066989709.mp4?t=1715970146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relax & Chill</h2>Acoustic guitar music by William King soothingly accompanies Hexton's gameplay, making the experience all the more relaxing and carefree.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/eda9e191ab578f08a8ac954e5b05c172.poster.avif?t=1715970146\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/eda9e191ab578f08a8ac954e5b05c172.webm?t=1715970146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/eda9e191ab578f08a8ac954e5b05c172.mp4?t=1715970146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Global competition</h2>See how well you fare versus the game's global playerbase. Will you be able to snatch and keep the highscore?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/4267e09b2e48c3bbf1d847a784fcb091.poster.avif?t=1715970146\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/4267e09b2e48c3bbf1d847a784fcb091.webm?t=1715970146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934400/extras/4267e09b2e48c3bbf1d847a784fcb091.mp4?t=1715970146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
